thread.title: Benjamin Lynn

author: Benjamin Lynn
title: Benjamin Lynn
text:
Local agent finder was rather simple to use and prompted to ask questions of the property managers I didn't even know would be a legitimate question.
Receiving all the data back in the 1 format made it easy to iron out the hidden costs and fees as well as get an onsite into who would look after us.
This went on to the point of receiving percentage cuts from the agents to stay competitive
